344
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,479
You'll be okay.

345
00:22:00,839 --> 00:22:12,680
They said that as long as you saw my face, you would bring me back.

346
00:22:13,359 --> 00:22:14,359
It's okay.

347
00:22:14,839 --> 00:22:16,078
It's okay.

348
00:22:16,079 --> 00:22:17,079
You'll be okay.

349
00:22:18,119 --> 00:22:19,160
Buzhen.

350
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:20,880
Buzhen.

351
00:22:22,439 --> 00:22:24,160
