556
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:31,280
Give my son back!

557
00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:33,759
Wait!

558
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:35,039
I'll kill you!

559
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:37,478
