729
00:42:05,719 --> 00:42:07,360
Great Khan won't bewilder me.

730
00:42:08,439 --> 00:42:09,519
Don't worry, Tegin.

731
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:12,199
I promise that I'll be back with the herb safely.

732
00:42:13,080 --> 00:42:14,080
Okay.

